#Task 1: Basic tasks

 ls
contest of a directory appear
ls command gives a list of contents in a directory

pwd
A directory
pwd goes to the current directory

mkdir workspace 
cd workspace

ls workspace

touch README.md 

cp README.md CHANGELOG.md/

#Task 2: Absolute and relative tasks

touch exercise.md
mv exercise.md /tmp
cd /tmp
rm exercise.md

#Task 3: cat commands

touch umuzi.md recruits.md cohort.md

nano umuzi.md
nano recruits.md
nano cohort.md

cat umuzi.md recruits.md cohort.md

cat umuzi.md recruits.md cohort.md > summary.md

nano summary.md

#Task 4:The locate command

locate umuzi
locate umuzi > search_result.md

